data.description: Discover the epitome of comfort and elegance in this stunning home tucked away on a quiet cul-de-sac in sought-after Piedmont South. The impressive two-story family room, complete with a cozy fireplace and built-in shelving, creates a warm and inviting gathering space. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring an oversized center island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast room with French doors that open to a charming paver patio. Enjoy the convenience of an office with double-door entry, providing a quiet and productive workspace. Formal living and dining rooms offer additional spaces for entertaining and special occasions. The large primary bedroom boasts a vaulted ceiling and a spacious en-suite bathroom with an oversized shower and a separate soaking tub, creating a luxurious retreat. The lower level is an entertainment haven, featuring a rec room with a wet bar and wine fridge, a media room with a screen, projector, and surround sound, a full bathroom, 2 bonus rooms, and French doors that open to the backyard. This home has an ideal location near Rts 66 & 15 for easy commuting, as well as proximity to great restaurants, shopping, and a variety of amenities. ACCEPTING BACK-UP OFFERS    Open House Sunday, November 19th 2023 from 1pm - 3pm
